snippet.title: Puke | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you ready for a thrilling and suspenseful adventure? Presenting Skyfect's new project, Puke! In this game, you take on the role of a journalist, observing your surroundings and taking valuable notes. Only then can you uncover the depths of the town of Frieden.

Puke Website : https://www.playpuke.com/

Skyfect Website: http://skyfect.com/

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2640130/Puke/?l=english
